Path: This week in Nu #46
Content:
arashout removed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2147] duplicate method in the Value API
, cleaned up the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2131] ``fetch``
 implementation
, improved the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2113] ``rm``
 command
, better 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2105] aligned tables for 
``ls``
JosephTLyons made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2143] ``last``
 more iterator-friendly
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2137] ``from vcf``
 more iterator-friendly
, improved the logic for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2112] ``last``
andrasio added some 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2140] new ways to do 
``str substring``
, added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2123] ``move column``
 command
almindor made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2129] path autocompletions work in more cases
pag4k moved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2128] duration to nanoseconds
 in preparation for timing commands
fdncred cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2122] special characters in prompts
jonathandturner and josephtlyons made 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2120] ``every``
 streamable
jonathandturenr also 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2111] fixed buffering in the 
``lines``
 command
, fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/21080] crash in the parser
, added an 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2106] ``if``
 command
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2102] ``str length``
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2101] ``split chars``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2100] ``each --numbered``
philip-peterson fixed parsing of 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2103] barewords and words with partial quoting
